---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="prose mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-24">
    <h1>Refund &amp; Billing Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <p>CampSoon uses prepaid points for successful campsite bookings. Creating campsite monitors is free, and points are only deducted when CampSoon helps you successfully book a campsite.</p>

    <h3>1. Point Deductions</h3>
    <p>Each successful campsite booking uses exactly 1,000 points. Points used for a successful booking are final and non-refundable.</p>

    <h3>2. 14-Day Refund Window for Unused Points</h3>
    <p>If you purchase a point package and have not used any points from that purchase, you may request a refund within 14 calendar days of your payment date.</p>

    <h3>3. Technical Errors &amp; System Discrepancies</h3>
    <p>If points are deducted because of a CampSoon technical error and no campsite was successfully booked, contact us with the relevant account and booking details. We will review the issue and restore points or refund the affected transaction when appropriate.</p>

    <h3>4. Contact</h3>
    <p>Send refund and billing requests to <strong>support@campsoon.com</strong> with your payment receipt and the email address used for your CampSoon account. Approved card refunds are returned to the original payment method and may take 3-5 business days to appear, depending on your card issuer.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
